{"tid":738033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE放榜日浸大天橋現「同學勿近」直幡","createTime":"2018-07-11T08:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T03:21:50.000Z","uid":63183,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc180570704f0170016316496b153855bd1583b","tid":738033,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/163640_6f8248d8019cc0fe4ca34f42f1f281f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F163640_6f8248d8019cc0fe4ca34f42f1f281f1.jpg&h=266be71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDSE放榜，同學仔還有機會改選大學聯招排序，各大院校也想盡攬尖子精英加盟，但此時此刻，年初曾爆普通話豁免率風波的浸會大學外一條行人天橋，今午(11日)突然出現一條黑底藍字「同學勿近」直幡，由於直幡由橋面伸延至迴旋樓梯，非常顯眼，不少人也駐足研究。<br />\n<br />\n在浸大普通話考試風波中，被判停學8日的浸大中醫系學生陳樂行，早前設立Facebook專頁「浸大山神」稱要光復浸大。該專頁今午就圖文並茂發貼稱，文憑試放榜日，浸大附近一道天橋乍現「同學勿近」直幡，呼籲考生遠離浸大，免受其普通話畢業要求及禁睇GPA等校政折磨。暫時未有人親認是掛幡人，而最新消息是該條天橋由浸大管理，基於安全理由，浸大稱已將直幡拆除。<br />\n<br />\n【突發】文憑試放榜日，香港浸會大學附近一道天橋乍現「同學勿近」直幡， 呼籲考生遠離浸大，免受其普通話畢業要求、全人教獄、禁睇 GPA 等混亂校政折磨。<br />\n<br />\nBreaking: Amid the release of Hong Kong Diploma of Secondary Education Examination (HKDSE) results, a banner reads &ldquo;Fellow students keep out&rdquo; appeared all of a sudden on a footbridge at the Hong Kong Baptist University (HKBU), calling on DSE candidates to stay away from BU and protect themselves from the University&rsquo;s torturous and misaligned policies such as Mandarin exit requirement, whole person education and withholding students&rsquo; grade point averages (GPA).<br />\n0"},{"pid":"6188ab01fb210ec128994024812428cbe057d1c3","tid":738033,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170263e5455a78f3866b22c24618775e1a8a69ca","tid":738033,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05e7b624e723a6fce0a6690c03a9107c530b35f","tid":738033,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc6ac2bdb2de55ee3accc9fda21211083cc4e88","tid":738033,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b716244c76ffc943d19f65272ac16f9a9571004b","tid":738033,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:43:57.000Z","msg":"同学勿近"},{"pid":"8aac136fada0cf6728325d95c4a2c6ec6351b979","tid":738033,"uid":92042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfb992c923b83d0cf47ee4842f5e854533b2387","tid":738033,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/photos/a.1636843183272848.1073741829.1569129996710834/1943431309280699/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkbumountaingod%2Fphotos%2Fa.1636843183272848.1073741829.1569129996710834%2F1943431309280699%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=JTRu4UmWOKpqXX3Vlp%2FPAQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=edba3ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/photos/a.1636843183272848.1073741829.1569129996710834/1943431309280699/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"2ebf239c6e8cbaf5be34887b4d0c571f9ce1c604","tid":738033,"uid":63183,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"6bc6ac2bdb2de55ee3accc9fda21211083cc4e88","tid":738033,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"寫畀香